ASoC: cs42l42: Correct definition of CS42L42_ADC_PDN_MASK

The definition of CS42L42_ADC_PDN_MASK was incorrectly defined
as the HP_PDN bit.

Fixes: 2c394ca79604 ("ASoC: Add support for CS42L42 codec")
